1
00:00:07,134 --> 00:00:11,571
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

2
00:00:11,639 --> 00:00:15,166
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

3
00:00:15,242 --> 00:00:18,678
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

4
00:00:18,746 --> 00:00:22,341
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh! Just go my way</i>

5
00:00:22,416 --> 00:00:25,681
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

6
00:00:25,753 --> 00:00:27,687
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>

7
00:00:29,490 --> 00:00:32,425
<i>Down a difficult road</i>
<i>filled with endless struggles</i>

8
00:00:32,493 --> 00:00:36,293
<i>Where do you think you are going</i>
<i>following someone else's map?</i>

9
00:00:36,697 --> 00:00:43,535
<i>An insightful crow comes along</i>
<i>to tear up the map</i>

10
00:00:43,771 --> 00:00:50,836
<i>Now open your eyes and</i>
<i>take a look at the truth (Yeah!)</i>

11
00:00:51,145 --> 00:00:57,277
<i>There's nothing to lose,</i>
<i>so let's GO!!!</i>

12
00:00:57,418 --> 00:01:01,684
<i>We are Fighting Dreamers aiming high</i>

13
00:01:01,755 --> 00:01:05,350
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>don't care what people think about them</i>

14
00:01:05,426 --> 00:01:08,759
<i>Fighting Dreamers</i>
<i>follow what they believe</i>

15
00:01:08,829 --> 00:01:12,458
<i>Oli Oli Oli Oh!</i>
<i>Just go my way</i>

16
00:01:12,533 --> 00:01:16,128
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

17
00:01:16,203 --> 00:01:19,695
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best!</i>

18
00:01:19,773 --> 00:01:23,368
<i>Right here right now (Bang)</i>
<i>Hit it straight like a line drive!</i>

19
00:01:23,444 --> 00:01:27,540
<i>Right here right now (Burn)</i>
<i>We're gonna do it and do our best! BANG!</i>

20
00:01:30,862 --> 00:01:35,595
For a start, wake up
that medium kid.

21
00:01:35,801 --> 00:01:36,961
It will release that Jutsu!

22
00:01:37,035 --> 00:01:38,468
How do we go about waking him?!

23
00:01:38,570 --> 00:01:41,403
Give him a good punch!

24
00:01:44,009 --> 00:01:44,805
But with that said...

25
00:01:44,876 --> 00:01:47,777
I'm not particularly good
at transformations...

26
00:01:48,013 --> 00:01:48,741
Huh?

27
00:01:48,814 --> 00:01:53,877
So you will act as my will
and make the Sign!

28
00:01:54,352 --> 00:01:56,183
Time for a combined transformation!

29
00:01:56,922 --> 00:02:01,621
We got to have fangs and claws!
Let's go!

30
00:02:02,094 --> 00:02:04,255
Transform!

31
00:02:16,007 --> 00:02:22,708
<i>Beyond the Limit of Darkness and Light</i>

32
00:02:26,218 --> 00:02:27,913
F-Fox?

33
00:02:57,349 --> 00:02:59,078
What a battle...

34
00:03:01,720 --> 00:03:04,154
<i>I can't call this place safe either, huh...</i>

35
00:03:05,090 --> 00:03:06,853
Darn it!

36
00:03:07,125 --> 00:03:09,059
His power is increasing
more and more!

37
00:03:09,628 --> 00:03:12,563
Chief! We got to hurry up and rouse
that guy out of his sleep!

38
00:03:18,737 --> 00:03:20,364
I know that!

39
00:03:21,773 --> 00:03:23,468
Here goes...!

40
00:03:27,913 --> 00:03:28,902
Go to hell!

41
00:03:44,596 --> 00:03:47,030
All right! Now!

42
00:03:47,098 --> 00:03:47,928
Okay!

43
00:03:53,538 --> 00:03:55,005
Wake the hell up!

44
00:04:00,345 --> 00:04:01,710
You jerk...

45
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:03,606
All right!

46
00:04:03,682 --> 00:04:06,515
Not that much time has passed
since the medium went to sleep!

47
00:04:06,585 --> 00:04:09,679
In that state,
one blow should be enough!

48
00:04:12,157 --> 00:04:13,818
Darn!

49
00:04:13,892 --> 00:04:17,293
It hasn't been long since I emerged!

50
00:04:19,764 --> 00:04:21,823
The Jutsu has been dissolved!

51
00:04:26,838 --> 00:04:28,738
Even if the Playing Possum Jutsu
is dissolved,

52
00:04:28,807 --> 00:04:30,798
he's still putting on the pressure?

53
00:04:40,852 --> 00:04:43,480
<i>That guy interfered with my Jutsu...?!</i>

54
00:04:46,424 --> 00:04:48,289
<i>Sand Coffin!</i>

55
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:50,453
- Pop!
- Yeah!

56
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,695
It's the chief's tongue...

57
00:04:54,132 --> 00:04:55,724
Don't take me for a fool!

58
00:05:06,578 --> 00:05:07,602
Darn!

59
00:05:08,747 --> 00:05:11,978
What kind of strength
does this guy possess?

60
00:05:12,083 --> 00:05:13,516
This doesn't look good...!

61
00:05:13,585 --> 00:05:17,919
Both Naruto and I have already
completely disgorged our Chakra!

62
00:05:21,259 --> 00:05:25,992
You will be killed by me!
I will not cease to exist!

63
00:05:30,368 --> 00:05:32,063
Leaf Hurricanes!

64
00:05:43,615 --> 00:05:46,140
Besides just the Sound Ninja,
I wouldn't have imagined that

65
00:05:46,217 --> 00:05:49,277
this many of the Sand Jonin
would enter into the village, too!

66
00:05:49,688 --> 00:05:54,125
Well, it's understandable.
This is what is called war.

67
00:05:58,296 --> 00:05:59,285
It's taking much too long.

68
00:06:00,065 --> 00:06:03,865
It's impossible for a battle
between Shinobi to last this long.

69
00:06:04,536 --> 00:06:06,504
What the heck is happening inside?

70
00:06:20,085 --> 00:06:22,349
<i>You're still grabbing my arm...</i>

71
00:06:22,420 --> 00:06:24,149
<i>I can't use my Jutsu this way...</i>

72
00:06:25,590 --> 00:06:28,684
Come on,
let go of me once and for all.

73
00:06:38,570 --> 00:06:44,099
I'm not letting your ambitions
interfere with the village... any longer...

74
00:06:44,275 --> 00:06:49,338
There's no stopping my ambitions!
You will die here!

75
00:06:50,048 --> 00:06:52,209
You old dotard...

76
00:06:52,884 --> 00:06:54,875
As the Third Hokage,

77
00:06:54,953 --> 00:06:59,481
are you saying you still have
the power to save this village?

78
00:07:00,792 --> 00:07:05,229
Do you understand...
the current situation?!

79
00:07:11,703 --> 00:07:15,264
Many Hidden Sand Shinobi and
my subordinates

80
00:07:15,340 --> 00:07:19,276
have infiltrated this village.

81
00:07:28,686 --> 00:07:32,122
Your side... the Leaf Shinobi...

82
00:07:32,190 --> 00:07:35,626
will be annihilated down to
every last woman and child!

83
00:07:36,227 --> 00:07:39,196
I will accomplish the destruction
of the Hidden Leaf Village!

84
00:07:53,311 --> 00:07:54,437
It's empty inside!

85
00:07:54,546 --> 00:07:55,638
There's nobody there!

86
00:07:56,281 --> 00:07:57,407
That's very strange...

87
00:07:57,649 --> 00:07:58,547
Huh?

88
00:07:58,883 --> 00:08:01,784
Why is there so little resistance
when we've closed in

89
00:08:01,853 --> 00:08:04,321
all the way to the center
of the Hidden Leaf Village?

90
00:08:05,156 --> 00:08:06,054
That's...

91
00:08:06,291 --> 00:08:10,694
And also... there's not one woman
or child in sight.

92
00:08:10,762 --> 00:08:12,161
What is the reason for that?

93
00:08:27,512 --> 00:08:28,479
Huh?!

94
00:08:29,614 --> 00:08:31,013
Konohamaru?

95
00:08:31,182 --> 00:08:33,514
What's the matter, Konohamaru?

96
00:08:35,487 --> 00:08:36,784
I gotta use the toilet.

97
00:08:37,355 --> 00:08:38,947
M-Me too...

98
00:08:39,691 --> 00:08:40,885
I do too...

99
00:08:47,465 --> 00:08:50,195
K-Konohamaru...!

100
00:08:51,336 --> 00:08:53,236
This is an emergency situation!

101
00:08:53,304 --> 00:08:55,932
If the enemy finds us,
it will cost us!

102
00:08:56,307 --> 00:08:58,673
Go back to the other room
and stay quiet!

103
00:08:59,344 --> 00:09:03,280
I-It's not that... I gotta pee!

104
00:09:03,348 --> 00:09:04,645
Hold it!

105
00:09:05,683 --> 00:09:08,083
I don't think I can hold it...

106
00:09:10,488 --> 00:09:14,322
Gimme a break.
In that case, come along with me...

107
00:09:15,159 --> 00:09:16,091
Can't hold it!

108
00:09:17,228 --> 00:09:18,388
Can't! Can't hold...!

109
00:10:01,072 --> 00:10:02,096
That's...

110
00:10:02,974 --> 00:10:04,271
At last, huh...

111
00:10:15,553 --> 00:10:19,512
I'll get revenge for you
no matter what...

112
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:22,726
Hayate.

113
00:10:26,097 --> 00:10:27,587
That's the signal. Let's go!

114
00:10:27,832 --> 00:10:28,491
Roger!

115
00:10:38,943 --> 00:10:42,811
You don't get it, do you, Orochimaru?

116
00:10:45,750 --> 00:10:49,846
Don't underestimate the Shinobi
of this Village!

117
00:10:56,228 --> 00:10:57,286
Are you all right?

118
00:10:58,564 --> 00:10:59,588
Yeah...

119
00:10:59,698 --> 00:11:01,563
Is that... the last?

120
00:11:01,700 --> 00:11:03,895
Yes, the evacuation is complete!

121
00:11:04,603 --> 00:11:07,595
W-What's happening?

122
00:11:07,940 --> 00:11:10,602
The Village Hidden in the Leaves
has an instruction manual

123
00:11:10,676 --> 00:11:12,803
outlining what to do in case of
a sneak attack by the enemy.

124
00:11:13,078 --> 00:11:16,980
Step One:
Eliminate the enemy's sneak attack force.

125
00:11:17,382 --> 00:11:19,942
In case one is unable
to eliminate them,

126
00:11:20,219 --> 00:11:22,779
proceed immediately to Step Two.

127
00:11:23,422 --> 00:11:26,186
The immediate evacuation
of noncombatants!

128
00:11:26,592 --> 00:11:31,222
Evacuate the women and children
to shelters around the village!

129
00:11:31,864 --> 00:11:34,628
When that has been completed,
proceed to Step Three!

130
00:11:35,033 --> 00:11:36,625
Step Three...?

131
00:11:37,135 --> 00:11:39,000
Through the collective strength
and efforts of the Village,

132
00:11:39,071 --> 00:11:40,436
eliminate the enemy!

133
00:11:40,772 --> 00:11:41,796
In that case...!

134
00:11:43,208 --> 00:11:46,041
The counteroffensive... starts now!

135
00:11:57,890 --> 00:12:00,620
We will not allow you to take
even one step beyond this point!

136
00:12:17,042 --> 00:12:18,009
<i>Sakura!</i>

137
00:12:18,877 --> 00:12:22,506
<i>Rescue Sakura,</i>
<i>if it's the last thing you do!</i>

138
00:12:23,148 --> 00:12:26,379
<i>I'll protect Sakura no matter what!</i>

139
00:12:35,060 --> 00:12:39,520
You will be killed by me.
I will not cease to exist.

140
00:12:39,898 --> 00:12:41,126
<i>My back is against the wall...</i>

141
00:12:41,199 --> 00:12:43,827
<i>I have to hurry up</i>
<i>and stop that Demon Raccoon...</i>

142
00:12:46,471 --> 00:12:47,495
<i>Please...</i>

143
00:12:49,708 --> 00:12:51,608
<i>Just a small amount is fine...</i>

144
00:12:52,511 --> 00:12:53,671
<i>Give me...</i>

145
00:13:05,157 --> 00:13:06,089
<i>some Chakra!</i>

146
00:13:32,384 --> 00:13:34,784
What are you doing...?
There's only one opponent!

147
00:13:47,099 --> 00:13:49,533
Hyuga is the magnum force
of the Leaf Village.

148
00:13:49,601 --> 00:13:50,932
Don't forget that!

149
00:13:54,506 --> 00:13:59,000
M-My... body... is immobilized...

150
00:14:00,512 --> 00:14:02,377
Is this the first time
you're experiencing

151
00:14:02,447 --> 00:14:04,972
the Leaf's hidden technique,
Shadow Paralysis Jutsu?

152
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:07,844
Well, take this too while I'm at it...

153
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:12,412
The Leaf's hidden technique...
Shadow Strangle Jutsu!

154
00:14:17,295 --> 00:14:18,887
Expansion Jutsu!

155
00:14:26,171 --> 00:14:28,139
Mind Destruction Jutsu!

156
00:14:32,844 --> 00:14:33,811
W-What's this?!

157
00:14:34,713 --> 00:14:36,340
My body is... all on its own...!

158
00:14:36,481 --> 00:14:37,812
S-Stop...

159
00:14:38,383 --> 00:14:39,315
Stop!

160
00:14:46,658 --> 00:14:48,489
Reminds me of the old days!

161
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:49,818
Yeah!

162
00:14:50,796 --> 00:14:53,458
The original Ino Shika Cho Trio reunites!

163
00:14:59,004 --> 00:15:00,471
Kuromaru... let's go

164
00:15:00,539 --> 00:15:01,403
Right!

165
00:15:02,641 --> 00:15:04,199
In order to protect the village,

166
00:15:04,276 --> 00:15:08,576
all the Leaf Shinobi will risk
their lives fighting

167
00:15:10,816 --> 00:15:17,949
Real strength doesn't lie
in the mastering of all Jutsu!

168
00:15:20,392 --> 00:15:22,553
The poison in my body is...

169
00:15:23,361 --> 00:15:26,455
Don't move, Shino.
I inserted my Parasitic Insects.

170
00:15:27,532 --> 00:15:28,794
They are removing the poison.

171
00:15:29,734 --> 00:15:30,496
Dad...

172
00:15:32,938 --> 00:15:36,169
I believe I taught this
to you too, in the past...

173
00:15:36,575 --> 00:15:38,975
It is when one protects
someone important...

174
00:15:39,478 --> 00:15:43,346
that the true strength of
the Shinobi will emerge!

175
00:15:46,218 --> 00:15:48,743
<i>I will protect everyone!</i>

176
00:15:53,725 --> 00:15:55,886
Here I come! You idiot raccoon!

177
00:15:55,961 --> 00:15:57,360
Die...!

178
00:16:03,201 --> 00:16:04,168
Darn...

179
00:16:05,871 --> 00:16:07,805
Darn it!

180
00:16:36,067 --> 00:16:37,125
D-Did he win?

181
00:16:38,203 --> 00:16:40,000
<i>A simple head blow...</i>

182
00:16:40,205 --> 00:16:42,969
<i>His manner of fighting</i>
<i>is incredibly clumsy,</i>

183
00:16:43,041 --> 00:16:46,943
<i>but to think that he could squeeze out</i>
<i>Chakra at that critical stage.</i>

184
00:16:47,846 --> 00:16:51,509
<i>I've never seen a knucklehead Ninja</i>
<i>like him before, but...</i>

185
00:16:51,583 --> 00:16:54,677
<i>he sure is the first phenomenal kid</i>
<i>I've seen in a long time.</i>

186
00:16:56,421 --> 00:16:59,515
<i>It's too bad that I can't see this through</i>
<i>to the end,</i>

187
00:17:00,225 --> 00:17:02,887
<i>but I've reached my limit.</i>

188
00:17:03,295 --> 00:17:06,059
Gamakichi, let's head home!

189
00:17:06,131 --> 00:17:07,792
Okay! Pop!

190
00:17:35,193 --> 00:17:39,061
As might be expected, even I...
am empty now...

191
00:17:40,932 --> 00:17:42,365
You are too, aren't you?

192
00:17:43,201 --> 00:17:48,468
We're much alike...
let's make this time the last!

193
00:17:52,744 --> 00:17:53,802
It appears that...

194
00:17:54,212 --> 00:18:01,618
I don't have the strength left
to yank out your entire soul.

195
00:18:02,387 --> 00:18:06,016
However, your ambition ends here!

196
00:18:06,258 --> 00:18:07,156
Not yet!

197
00:18:07,726 --> 00:18:10,160
There's no stopping my ambition!

198
00:18:10,462 --> 00:18:12,157
I have a suitable punishment for you

199
00:18:12,230 --> 00:18:17,793
who have become addicted to the Jutsu
and who have overindulged in the Jutsu!

200
00:18:17,869 --> 00:18:21,600
I will take all your Jutsu away with me!

201
00:18:21,673 --> 00:18:22,765
What did you say?!

202
00:18:30,482 --> 00:18:31,278
There!

203
00:18:31,916 --> 00:18:33,076
Don't tell me that?

204
00:18:33,218 --> 00:18:35,186
Stop that!

205
00:18:38,623 --> 00:18:40,056
Seal!

206
00:18:49,534 --> 00:18:52,059
My... My arms...

207
00:18:55,006 --> 00:18:58,601
Now... you can no longer use
either of your arms.

208
00:18:59,344 --> 00:19:03,576
And since you can't use your arms,
you can't weave Signs.

209
00:19:04,149 --> 00:19:07,084
You no longer possess Ninjutsu!

210
00:19:09,754 --> 00:19:14,214
Your ambition of crushing
the Hidden Leaf... dies right here!

211
00:19:14,893 --> 00:19:18,624
You old dotard!
Give me back my arms!

212
00:19:19,731 --> 00:19:22,427
Orochimaru, you fool...

213
00:19:23,101 --> 00:19:26,093
It's unfortunate that
we can't leave together,

214
00:19:26,571 --> 00:19:28,095
but, my disciple...

215
00:19:29,374 --> 00:19:32,207
let's meet in the other world one day.

216
00:19:32,377 --> 00:19:34,402
You old dotard...
whose life is hanging by a thread!

217
00:19:34,479 --> 00:19:38,142
How dare you!
How dare you take away my Jutsu!

218
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:05,502
<i>In places where the Leaf dances,</i>
<i>a fire burns...</i>

219
00:20:11,148 --> 00:20:14,049
<i>The shadow of the fire</i>
<i>will illuminate the Village...</i>

220
00:20:35,906 --> 00:20:39,069
<i>And once more the Leaf will sprout...</i>

221
00:21:10,407 --> 00:21:14,207
<i>A cycle of hardship, right?</i>

222
00:21:15,345 --> 00:21:19,179
<i>Inside, we were crying, right?</i>

223
00:21:20,717 --> 00:21:28,590
<i>But the one thing we won't give up</i>
<i>is the dream we've chosen, right?</i>

224
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:31,528
<i>It's a secondary role,</i>

225
00:21:34,464 --> 00:21:37,331
<i>a role in the shadows</i>

226
00:21:37,868 --> 00:21:42,965
<i>But in reaching for that dream,</i>

227
00:21:43,040 --> 00:21:48,569
<i>let us stay centered,</i>
<i>let us stay true</i>

228
00:21:48,845 --> 00:21:53,475
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we hung on without giving up</i>

229
00:21:53,550 --> 00:21:58,453
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we kept coming back up</i>

230
00:21:58,522 --> 00:22:07,692
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we believed and dreamed</i>

231
00:22:08,298 --> 00:22:13,497
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've seen fools</i>

232
00:22:13,670 --> 00:22:18,937
<i>Over and over,</i>
<i>we've stood in the shadows of others</i>

233
00:22:20,777 --> 00:22:30,709
<i>Now, it's our turn...</i>
<i>Let us bask in our dreams</i>

234
00:22:38,662 --> 00:22:40,061
Lord Third Hokage...

235
00:22:40,430 --> 00:22:43,160
The ambition that you had
seems to have been passed on

236
00:22:43,233 --> 00:22:47,932
to the young Shinobi
in the Village Hidden in the Leaves.

237
00:22:49,039 --> 00:22:53,567
The flame in their hearts will
burn large and strong in the future.

238
00:22:53,644 --> 00:22:57,774
And someday,
they will illuminate this Village...

239
00:22:57,848 --> 00:23:00,078
just as you have done for us!

240
00:23:01,585 --> 00:23:04,748
Next time:
"The Third Hokage, Forever..."
